headline: Western Sahara: US goes on offensive at UN to defend autonomy under Moroccan sovereignty
description: On Thursday, the UN Security Council is set to vote on a draft resolution aimed at clarifying the territory's status, which is contested by Rabat and the pro-independence Polisario Front. The US-backed motion aims to boost the prospect of an autonomous status under Moroccan sovereignty.
